{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/TIL_43_210217/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"65-mongostore-and-middlewares\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#65-mongostore-and-middlewares\" aria-label=\"65 mongostore and middlewares permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[6.5] MongoStore and Middlewares</h1>\n<h3 id=\"유저-정보를-쿠키에-계속-유지하는-법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4%EC%97%90-%EA%B3%84%EC%86%8D-%EC%9C%A0%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"유저 정보를 쿠키에 계속 유지하는 법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>유저 정보를 쿠키에 계속 유지하는 법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>로그인 했다 해도, 서버를 껐다 키거나, 새로고침하면 쿠키가 남아있지 않고 날아감</li>\n<li>따라서, 유저 정보를 Mongodb에 저장해서, X라는 유저가 지금 로그인 해있다는 걸 쿠키에 계속 남겨줘야 함</li>\n<li>공식 문서 참고 : <a href=\"https://github.com/jdesboeufs/connect-mongo#readme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/jdesboeufs/connect-mongo#readme</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"1-connect-mongo-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-connect-mongo-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 connect mongo 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. connect-mongo 설치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm install connect-mongo</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-import-connect-mongo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-import-connect-mongo\" aria-label=\"2 import connect mongo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. import connect-mongo</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">import MongoStore from &quot;connect-mongo</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-mongodb에-연결해줌\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-mongodb%EC%97%90-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%B4%EC%A4%8C\" aria-label=\"3 mongodb에 연결해줌 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. mongodb에 연결해줌</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>일단, 공식문서에 따라서 new MongoStore 변수에 담음 </li>\n<li>const CookieStore = new MongoStore(session)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-appusesession에-store-key값-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-appusesession%EC%97%90-store-key%EA%B0%92-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"4 appusesession에 store key값 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. app.use(session)에 store key값 추가</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>아래 코드는 공식문서를 따른것</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">mongoose.connection</code>을 통해, db에 연결!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">app.use(\nsession({\nsecret: process.env.COOKIE_SECRET,\nresave: true,\nsaveUninitialized: false,\nstore: new CookieStore({ mongooseConnection: mongoose.connection }),\n})\n);</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"routes-접근-제한\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#routes-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C\" aria-label=\"routes 접근 제한 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Routes 접근 제한</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>이미 로그인한 유저는 join 화면에 접근이 안되어야함</li>\n<li>로그인하지 않은 유저는, 볼 수 없는 페이지가 있어야함(프로필 수정 등)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"1-middleware-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-middleware-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 middleware 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. middleware 생성</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>로그인된 user 정보가 있는지 <code class=\"language-text\">req.user</code>로 체크하고, 있는경우와 없는경우에 routing 시킬 곳을 설정</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-onlypubclic-미들웨어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-onlypubclic-%EB%AF%B8%EB%93%A4%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"2 onlypubclic 미들웨어 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. onlyPubclic 미들웨어</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>로그인 안된 유저의 접근을 막는 페이지 코드</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const onlyPublic = (req, res, next) =&gt; {\nif (req.user) {\nres.redirect(routes.home);\n} else {\nnext();\n}\n};</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"3-onlyprivate-미들웨어\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-onlyprivate-%EB%AF%B8%EB%93%A4%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4\" aria-label=\"3 onlyprivate 미들웨어 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. onlyPrivate 미들웨어</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>로그인한 유저의 접근을 막는 페이지 코드</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">export const onlyPrivate = (req, res, next) =&gt; {\nif (req.user) {\nnext();\n} else {\nres.redirect(routes.home);\n}\n};</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-해당-코드들을-router-파일들의-필요부분에-삽입\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%ED%95%B4%EB%8B%B9-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-router-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%EB%B6%80%EB%B6%84%EC%97%90-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85\" aria-label=\"4 해당 코드들을 router 파일들의 필요부분에 삽입 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 해당 코드들을, router 파일들의 필요부분에 삽입</h3>","excerpt":"6.5 MongoStore and Middlewares 유저 정보를 쿠키에 계속 유지하는 법 로그인 했다 해도, 서버를 껐다 키거나, 새로고침하면 쿠키가 남아있지 않고 날아감 따라서, 유저 정보를 Mongodb에 저장해서, X라는 유저가 지금 로그인…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#65-mongostore-and-middlewares\">6.5 MongoStore and Middlewares</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#%EC%9C%A0%EC%A0%80-%EC%A0%95%EB%B3%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%BF%A0%ED%82%A4%EC%97%90-%EA%B3%84%EC%86%8D-%EC%9C%A0%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B2%95\">유저 정보를 쿠키에 계속 유지하는 법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#1-connect-mongo-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\">1. connect-mongo 설치</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#2-import-connect-mongo\">2. import connect-mongo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#3-mongodb%EC%97%90-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%B4%EC%A4%8C\">3. mongodb에 연결해줌</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#4-appusesession%EC%97%90-store-key%EA%B0%92-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\">4. app.use(session)에 store key값 추가</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#routes-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C\">Routes 접근 제한</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#1-middleware-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\">1. middleware 생성</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#2-onlypubclic-%EB%AF%B8%EB%93%A4%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4\">2. onlyPubclic 미들웨어</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#3-onlyprivate-%EB%AF%B8%EB%93%A4%EC%9B%A8%EC%96%B4\">3. onlyPrivate 미들웨어</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/TIL_43_210217/#4-%ED%95%B4%EB%8B%B9-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%84-router-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%EB%93%A4%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%84%EC%9A%94%EB%B6%80%EB%B6%84%EC%97%90-%EC%82%BD%EC%9E%85\">4. 해당 코드들을, router 파일들의 필요부분에 삽입</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/TIL_43_210217/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"TIL-210217","date":"Feb 17, 2021","tags":["TIL","connectMongo","mongostore"],"keywords":["dobedh","Donghyun Kim"],"update":"Jan 01, 0001"}}},"